  "body": {
    "view": {
      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><a href=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/pages/createpage.action?spaceKey=RFK24&amp;title=PxrPortalLight\" rel=\"nofollow\">PxrPortalLight</a> can provide great quality improvements over PxrDomeLight for interior scene renders. Portals also allow you to selectively use multiple Dome Lights in a scene, and use certain light filters that don't work with Dome Lights.. This document outlines the steps required to set up Portal Lights in Katana.</p><h3 id=\"PortalLightsinKatana-CreatingPortalLights\">Creating Portal Lights</h3><p>A Portal Light on its own will not contribute light to the scene. The Portal needs to be a child of a Dome Light to have any contribution. A Portal inherits parameters from the parent Dome and either multiplies or overrides those parameters if its own equivalent parameter is set.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-left-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-left\" width=\"800\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178489/rfkPortalLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532527&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=718\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/546178489/rfkPortalLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532527&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"718\" data-width=\"800\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"546178506\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"rfkPortalLights.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"546178489\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"4\" data-media-id=\"a289e625-f86b-4505-83f1-7de63152cf9b\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178489/rfkPortalLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532527&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=718 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/546178489/rfkPortalLights.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754531532527&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=800&amp;height=718 1x\"></span><h3 id=\"PortalLightsinKatana-LightFiltersandPortalLights\">Light Filters and Portal Lights</h3><p>Any light filter applied to a dome light will automatically be applied to that dome's portal lights.  Portal lights can also have their own light filters.</p><h3 id=\"PortalLightsinKatana-AdditionalNotes\">Additional Notes</h3><p>Changes to Portal Light position can be slow to update in Live Rendering. In such cases, you can improve performance by setting the 3D update mode to &quot;Pen-up&quot;.</p>"
    }
